
WEBVTT

01:16.290 --> 01:18.790
<b>我相信美国</b><b>
I believe in America.</b><b></b>

01:19.330 --> 01:22.140
<b>美国使我发了财</b><b>
America has made my fortune</b><b></b>

01:22.500 --> 01:25.860
<b>而我以美国方式教养我的女儿</b><b>
and I raised my daughter in the American fashion.</b><b></b>

01:26.660 --> 01:28.830
<b>我给她自由</b><b>
I give her freedom, but I taught her</b><b></b>

01:28.840 --> 01:32.110
<b>但也告诉她永远不要有辱家门</b><b>
never to dishonor her family.</b><b></b>

01:32.920 --> 01:36.120
<b>她交了位男友但不是意大利人</b><b>
She found a boyfriend. Not an Italian.</b><b></b>

01:36.130 --> 01:39.710
<b>她跟他去看电影 深夜才回家</b><b>
She went to the movies with him.</b><b></b>

01:39.990 --> 01:42.530
<b>我并没有责骂她</b><b>
She stayed out late. I didn't protest.</b><b></b>

01:42.730 --> 01:45.890
<b>两个月前他与另一个男孩</b><b>
Two months ago, he took her for a drive</b><b></b>

01:45.900 --> 01:48.190
<b>带她去兜风</b><b>
with another boyfriend.</b><b></b>

01:48.510 --> 01:51.220
<b>他们强灌她喝威士忌</b><b>
They made her drink whiskey</b><b></b>

01:51.240 --> 01:55.570
<b>然后他们想要占她便宜</b><b>
and then they tried to take advantage of her.</b><b></b>

01:55.670 --> 02:00.510
<b>她抵抗 她保住了名节</b><b>
She resisted.She kept her honor.</b><b></b>

02:01.090 --> 02:04.980
<b>于是他们像对动物般的毒打她</b><b>
So they beat her like an animal.</b><b></b>

02:06.050 --> 02:10.840
<b>当我到医院时 她的鼻梁断了</b><b>
When I went to the hospital, her nose was broken</b><b></b>

02:11.000 --> 02:13.110
<b>她的下巴被打碎了</b><b>
her jaw was shattered</b><b></b>

02:13.120 --> 02:16.270
<b>必须用钢丝绑着才不会掉下来</b><b>
held together by wire.</b><b></b>

02:17.690 --> 02:21.440
<b>她痛得不能哭</b><b>
She couldn't even weep because of the pain.</b><b></b>

02:23.330 --> 02:27.520
<b>但我却哭了 我为什么哭呢?</b><b>
But I wept. Why did I weep?</b><b></b>

02:29.410 --> 02:32.730
<b>我视她如珠如宝</b><b>
She was the light of my life.</b><b></b>

02:33.800 --> 02:35.860
<b>她长得很美丽</b><b>
Beautiful girl.</b><b></b>

02:39.130 --> 02:42.370
<b>现在她再也美丽不起来</b><b>
Now she will never be beautiful again.</b><b></b>

02:48.850 --> 02:50.400
<b>不好意思</b><b>
Sorry.</b><b></b>

02:58.370 --> 03:02.740
<b>我去报警 像个守法的美国人一样</b><b>
I went to the police like a good American.</b><b></b>

03:03.060 --> 03:05.770
<b>那两个男孩受到了审判</b><b>
These two boys were brought to trial.</b><b></b>

03:06.830 --> 03:12.290
<b>法官判他们有期徒刑三年但缓刑</b><b>
Ajudge sentence them to three years in prison and suspend their sentence.</b><b></b>

03:13.090 --> 03:15.680
<b>缓刑</b><b>
Suspended sentence.</b><b></b>

03:15.690 --> 03:19.020
<b>他们当天就没事了</b><b>
They went free that very day.</b><b></b>

03:20.250 --> 03:23.670
<b>我像个傻瓜似的站在法庭中</b><b>
I stood in the courtroom like a fool.</b><b></b>

03:23.680 --> 03:27.840
<b>而那两个混蛋竟朝着我笑</b><b>
And those two bastard, they smiled at me.</b><b></b>

03:28.470 --> 03:29.940
<b>于是我对我太太说</b><b>
Then I said to my wife, ''For justice</b><b></b>

03:29.950 --> 03:35.220
<b>为求公道 我们必须去找柯里昂阁下</b><b>
we must go to Don Corleone.''</b><b></b>

03:39.450 --> 03:43.290
<b>你去报警前为何不先来找我</b><b>
Why did you go to the police? Why didn't you come to me first?</b><b></b>

03:43.970 --> 03:45.860
<b>你要我怎么样</b><b>
What do you want of me?</b><b></b>

03:45.870 --> 03:49.930
<b>你尽管吩咐 但求你一定要帮我这个忙</b><b>
Tell me anything, but do what I beg you to do.</b><b></b>

03:50.210 --> 03:51.930
<b>帮你什么忙</b><b>
What is that?</b><b></b>

04:16.400 --> 04:18.420
<b>那个我办不到</b><b>
That I cannot do.</b><b></b>

04:19.570 --> 04:22.500
<b>你要什么 我都会给你</b><b>
I'll give you anything you ask.</b><b></b>

04:24.300 --> 04:26.200
<b>我们相识多年</b><b>
We've known each other many years, but this is the first time</b><b></b>

04:26.210 --> 04:30.100
<b>这是你第一次来找我帮忙</b><b>
you ever came to me for counsel or for help.</b><b></b>

04:30.940 --> 04:36.270
<b>我记不起你上次是何时 请我到你家去喝咖啡了</b><b>
I can't remember the last time that you invited me to your house for a cup of coffee</b><b></b>

04:37.290 --> 04:41.040
<b>何况我太太还是你独生女的教母</b><b>
even though my wife is godmother to your only child.</b><b></b>

04:41.370 --> 04:43.480
<b>我坦白说吧</b><b>
But let's be frank.</b><b></b>

04:43.490 --> 04:45.950
<b>你从来就不想要我的友谊</b><b>
You never wanted my friendship</b><b></b>

04:46.280 --> 04:50.170
<b>而且你害怕欠我人情</b><b>
and you were afraid to be in my debt.</b><b></b>

04:50.180 --> 04:52.850
<b>我不想卷入是非</b><b>
I didn't want to get into trouble.</b><b></b>

04:53.660 --> 04:55.590
<b>我了解</b><b>
I understand.</b><b></b>

04:56.570 --> 04:59.580
<b>你在美国发了财</b><b>
You found paradise in America.</b><b></b>

05:01.860 --> 05:03.540
<b>生意做的很好 生活过的很好</b><b>
You had a good trade, made a good living.</b><b></b>

05:03.550 --> 05:06.710
<b>有警察和法律保护你</b><b>
Police protected you, and there were courts of law.</b><b></b>

05:06.720 --> 05:09.250
<b>你不需要我这种朋友</b><b>
So you didn't need a friend like me.</b><b></b>

05:11.110 --> 05:14.450
<b>但是现在你来找我说</b><b>
But now you come to me and you say</b><b></b>

05:14.460 --> 05:17.470
<b>柯里昂阁下 请帮我主持公道</b><b>
''Don Corleone, give me justice.''</b><b></b>

05:18.930 --> 05:21.730
<b>但你对我一点尊重也没有</b><b>
But you don't ask with respect.</b><b></b>

05:21.920 --> 05:24.330
<b>你并不把我当朋友</b><b>
You don't offer friendship.</b><b></b>

05:24.660 --> 05:27.370
<b>你甚至不愿意喊我教父</b><b>
You don't even think to call me ''Godfather.''</b><b></b>

05:28.480 --> 05:31.900
<b>你在我女儿结婚当天来我家</b><b>
Instead, you come into my house on the day my daughter is to be married</b><b></b>

05:31.910 --> 05:35.150
<b>用钱收买我为你杀人</b><b>
and you ask me to do murder for money.</b><b></b>

05:35.160 --> 05:37.970
<b>我只是要求你主持公道</b><b>
I ask you for justice.</b><b></b>

05:37.980 --> 05:41.220
<b>那不是公道 你女儿还活着</b><b>
That is not justice. Your daughter is still alive.</b><b></b>

05:41.890 --> 05:46.300
<b>那么让他们像她一样受折磨</b><b>
They must suffer then as she suffers.</b><b></b>

05:47.500 --> 05:49.470
<b>我应该付你多少钱</b><b>
How much shall I pay you?</b><b></b>

06:04.390 --> 06:08.460
<b>包纳萨拉 包纳萨拉</b><b>
Bonasera.</b><b></b>

06:08.470 --> 06:12.820
<b>到底我做了什么让你这么的不尊重我</b><b>
What have I ever done to make you treat me so disrespectfully?</b><b></b>

06:13.680 --> 06:16.350
<b>如果你以朋友身分来找我</b><b>
If you'd come to me in friendship</b><b></b>

06:16.450 --> 06:21.260
<b>那么伤害你女儿的杂碎 就会受到折磨</b><b>
then the scum that ruined your daughter would be suffering this very day.</b><b></b>

06:22.020 --> 06:23.830
<b>你这种诚实人的敌人</b><b>
And if, by chance an honest man like yourself should make enemies</b><b></b>

06:23.840 --> 06:27.900
<b>也就是我的敌人</b><b>
then they would become my enemies.</b><b></b>

06:30.090 --> 06:32.770
<b>那么 他们就会害怕你</b><b>
And then they would fear you.</b><b></b>

06:36.520 --> 06:38.370
<b>当我的朋友</b><b>
Be my friend?</b><b></b>

06:42.640 --> 06:44.480
<b>教父</b><b>
Godfather.</b><b></b>

06:48.580 --> 06:50.080
<b>很好</b><b>
Good.</b><b></b>

06:51.670 --> 06:53.910
<b>他日我或许需要你的帮忙</b><b>
Someday, and that day may never come</b><b></b>

06:53.920 --> 06:56.690
<b>也可能不会有那么一天</b><b>
I'll call upon you to do a service for me.</b><b></b>

06:58.240 --> 07:01.510
<b>但在那一天到来之前</b><b>
But until that day</b><b></b>

07:02.230 --> 07:06.060
<b>收下这份公道做为小女结婚之礼</b><b>
accept this justice as a gift on my daughter's wedding day.</b><b></b>

07:06.560 --> 07:09.490
<b>谢谢 教父 别客气</b><b>
Grazie, Godfather.</b><b></b>

07:15.510 --> 07:19.610
<b>这件事交给… 克里曼沙</b><b>
Give this to Clemenza.</b><b></b>

07:21.070 --> 07:24.700
<b>我要用可康娜送纺郧逍训娜?</b><b>
I want reliable people people that aren't going to be carried away.</b><b></b>

07:24.710 --> 07:29.170
<b>我们不是谋杀犯 下手别太重</b><b>
I mean, we're not murderers in spite of what this undertaker says.</b><b></b>

07:54.200 --> 07:57.510
<b>- 麦克在哪? - 别担心 他一会就来</b><b>
- Where's Michael? - What? Don't worry. It's early. He'll be here.</b><b></b>

07:58.570 --> 08:01.380
<b>没有麦克我不照相</b><b>
We're not taking it.</b><b></b>

08:01.920 --> 08:05.940
<b>待会再拍</b><b>
We're not taking the picture without Michael.</b><b></b>

08:08.130 --> 08:10.460
<b>- 什么事? - 麦克的事</b><b>
- What's the matter, Sonny? - It's Michael.</b><b></b>

09:00.320 --> 09:02.300
<b>你好 巴西尼阁下</b><b>
Don Barzini.</b><b></b>

09:05.450 --> 09:07.860
<b>你认得我儿子吧</b><b></b>

09:18.480 --> 09:21.600
<b>保利 让我喝点酒</b><b>
Hey, Paulie! Let me have some wine.</b><b></b>

09:21.610 --> 09:24.440
<b>保利 再来点酒</b><b>
Paulie! More wine. Scusi, please.</b><b></b>

09:25.770 --> 09:29.320
<b>你看起来棒极了 你是裁判还是什么?</b><b>
You look ''terrif'' on the floor. What are you, a dance judge or something?</b><b></b>

09:29.330 --> 09:33.690
<b>闪开吧 到附近晃晃做你的工作</b><b>
Go take a walk around the neighborhood. Do your job.</b><b></b>

09:41.050 --> 09:44.090
<b>仙杜拉 帮个忙 别让孩子乱跑 好吗?</b><b>
Sandra, come on. Do me a favor. Watch the kids.</b><b></b>

09:44.100 --> 09:46.550
<b>- 你看好你自己 - 好吗?</b><b>
- Don't let 'em run wild. - You watch yourself, all right?</b><b></b>

10:08.240 --> 10:12.990
<b>两三万元小钞 全是现金</b><b>
Twenty or thirty grand. In small bills, cash.</b><b></b>

10:13.280 --> 10:15.780
<b>全在那个小丝袋里</b><b>
In that little silk purse.</b><b></b>

10:15.790 --> 10:19.430
<b>如果这是我的婚礼我就发财了</b><b>
If this was somebody else's wedding.</b><b></b>

10:19.440 --> 10:24.380
<b>保利 接住吧</b><b>
Hey, Paulie! I got two gobbagool gabagol and a prosciutto.</b><b></b>

10:24.830 --> 10:26.450
<b>你这个笨蛋</b><b>
Stupid jerk!</b><b></b>

10:34.850 --> 10:36.660
<b>怎么回事?</b><b>
Hey, what's the matter?</b><b></b>

10:49.140 --> 10:51.560
<b>我得回去工作了 汤姆</b><b>
Have to go back to work.</b><b></b>

10:51.570 --> 10:52.820
<b>这是婚礼的一部分</b><b>
It's part of the wedding.</b><b></b>

10:52.830 --> 10:56.100
<b>没有西西里人在女儿结婚那天 能拒绝任何的请求</b><b>
No Sicilian can refuse any request on his daughter's wedding day.</b><b></b>

11:01.390 --> 11:07.140
<b>柯里昂阁下能受邀到贵府 深感荣幸</b><b>
Don Corleone, I am honored and grateful that you have invited me to your home-</b><b></b>

11:09.550 --> 11:12.880
<b>你们在干什么?滚</b><b>
Get outta here.</b><b></b>

11:12.890 --> 11:15.080
<b>这是私人宴会 快滚</b><b>
This is a private party. Go on.</b><b></b>

11:15.930 --> 11:19.030
<b>这算什么? 是我妹妹的婚礼</b><b>
What is it? Hey, my sister's wedding.</b><b></b>

11:25.610 --> 11:28.500
<b>该死的联邦密探什么都不尊重</b><b>
Goddamn FBI don't respect nothin'.</b><b></b>

11:31.260 --> 11:35.320
<b>过来这 到这来!</b><b>
Hey, come here, come here. Come here!There.</b><b></b>

11:48.620 --> 11:53.340
<b>但最后他获假释去为美国作战</b><b>
But towards the end he was paroled to help with the American war effort.</b><b></b>

11:53.350 --> 11:56.460
<b>过去六个月他在我的糕饼店做事</b><b>
For the last six months, he's been working at my pastry shop.</b><b></b>

11:56.570 --> 11:59.240
<b>纳色利 我的朋友 我能为你做什么?</b><b>
Nazorine, my friend, what can I do for you?</b><b></b>

11:59.350 --> 12:01.290
<b>现在战争结束了</b><b>
Now that the war is over</b><b></b>

12:01.300 --> 12:05.270
<b>这男孩 安索 他们要把他遣返意大利</b><b>
this boy, Enzo, they want to repatriate him back to Italy.</b><b></b>

12:05.560 --> 12:11.320
<b>教父 我有个女儿她和安索…</b><b>
Godfather, I have a daughter. See, she and Enzo-</b><b></b>

12:11.640 --> 12:16.140
<b>你要安索留在这个国家 和你女儿成亲</b><b>
You want Enzo to stay in this country and you want your daughter to be married.</b><b></b>

12:17.200 --> 12:20.260
<b>你什么都了解 谢谢</b><b>
You understand everything.</b><b></b>

12:20.540 --> 12:23.470
<b>哈金先生 谢谢</b><b>
Mr. Hagen. Thank you.</b><b></b>

12:26.020 --> 12:28.910
<b>待会看看我为你女儿 做的结婚蛋糕</b><b>
And wait till you see the beautiful wedding cake I made for your daughter.</b><b></b>

12:28.920 --> 12:32.760
<b>这么高… 还有一对新人和天使</b><b>
Like this, with the bride and the groom and-</b><b></b>

12:38.080 --> 12:40.030
<b>- 这件事我该交给谁去办? - 别给我们这个选区</b><b>
- Who should I give this job to? - Not to our paisan.</b><b></b>

12:40.040 --> 12:46.150
<b>给别地区的犹太籍众议员</b><b>
Give it to a Jew congressman in another district.</b><b></b>

12:46.730 --> 12:48.530
<b>名单上还有谁</b><b>
Who else is on the list?</b><b></b>

12:53.890 --> 12:56.860
<b>你好 麦克 最近怎么样?</b><b>
Hey, Michael. How are you? Hello.</b><b></b>

13:16.390 --> 13:19.620
<b>路卡布拉西不在名单上 但他想要见你</b><b>
He's not on the list, but Luca Brasi wants to see you.</b><b></b>

13:25.640 --> 13:28.260
<b>这个有这个必要吗?</b><b>
Is this necessary?</b><b></b>

13:28.270 --> 13:31.860
<b>他没料到会受邀参加婚礼 所以要向你致谢</b><b>
He didn't expect to be invited to the wedding so he wanted to thank you.</b><b></b>

13:31.880 --> 13:33.720
<b>好吧</b><b>
All right.</b><b></b>

13:33.960 --> 13:39.690
<b>柯里昂阁下 在令媛婚礼这天</b><b>
Don Corleone, I am honored and grateful</b><b></b>

13:39.700 --> 13:42.230
<b>能受邀到贵府深感荣幸</b><b>
that you have invited me to your home on the wedding day of your daughter.</b><b></b>

13:42.390 --> 13:45.580
<b>希望他们早生贵子</b><b>
And may their first child be a masculine child.</b><b></b>

13:46.030 --> 13:47.830
<b>麦克</b><b>
Michael?</b><b></b>

13:49.220 --> 13:52.150
<b>那边的那个人在自言自语</b><b>
That man over there is talking to himself.</b><b></b>

13:52.730 --> 13:55.660
<b>看到那边那个吓人的家伙了吗?</b><b>
See that scary guy over there?</b><b></b>

13:55.720 --> 13:59.400
<b>他很叫人害怕 他是谁?叫什么名字</b><b>
He's a very scary guy.Who is he? What's his name?</b><b></b>

13:59.410 --> 14:04.600
<b>他叫做路卡布拉西 有时候替家父办事</b><b>
His name is Luca Brasi and he helps my father out sometimes.</b><b></b>

14:05.750 --> 14:07.650
<b>麦克 等一下 他过来了</b><b>
Wait a minute. He's coming over here.</b><b></b>

14:07.660 --> 14:09.540
<b>麦克</b><b>
Michael!</b><b></b>

14:10.610 --> 14:12.450
<b>汤姆</b><b>
Tom</b><b></b>

14:13.050 --> 14:14.930
<b>你气色好极了</b><b>
You look terrific!</b><b></b>

14:15.000 --> 14:17.030
<b>家兄汤姆哈金 这是凯亚当斯</b><b>
My brother Tom Hagen. This is Kay Adams.</b><b></b>

14:17.040 --> 14:18.830
<b>你好 你好</b><b>
How do you do? Nice to meet you.</b><b></b>

14:19.510 --> 14:22.050
<b>你父亲要见你</b><b>
Your father's been asking for you.</b><b></b>

14:22.590 --> 14:24.620
<b>- 幸会 - 幸会</b><b>
- Very nice to meet you. - Nice to meet you.I'll be there.</b><b></b>

14:27.030 --> 14:29.570
<b>若他是你哥哥 为何不同姓?</b><b>
If he's your brother, why does he have a different name?</b><b></b>

14:29.630 --> 14:35.610
<b>小时候在街上发现汤姆无家可归</b><b>
When my brother Sonny was a kid he found Tom Hagen in the street, and he had no home.</b><b></b>

14:35.930 --> 14:38.160
<b>所以家父收养了他</b><b>
So my father took him in</b><b></b>

14:39.400 --> 14:41.470
<b>从此他就和我们住在一起了</b><b>
and he's been with us ever since.</b><b></b>

14:42.440 --> 14:44.280
<b>他是个好律师</b><b>
He's a good lawyer.</b><b></b>

14:45.220 --> 14:49.980
<b>不是西西里人但我想他会当军师</b><b>
