30:25.930 --> 30:30.270
<b>我敢说俄国沙皇 也从未在马身上花那么大笔钱</b><b>
I'll bet Russian czars never paid that kind of dough for a single horse.</b><b></b>

30:30.280 --> 30:34.390
<b>达通 达通</b><b>
Khartoum.</b><b></b>

30:35.190 --> 30:40.460
<b>不过我不会用它们来比赛 我要它们当种马</b><b>
I'm not gonna race him, though. I'm gonna put him out to stud.</b><b></b>

30:41.310 --> 30:42.860
<b>- 谢谢 汤尼 - 不必客气</b><b>
