30:46.600 --> 30:49.750
<b>柯里昂是强尼的教父</b><b>
Mr. Corleone is Johnny's godfather.</b><b></b>

30:50.080 --> 30:54.620
<b>对意大利人而言 那是种宗教上神圣的亲密关系</b><b>
To the Italian people, that's a very religious sacred, close relationship.</b><b></b>

30:54.630 --> 30:55.880
<b>我很敬重这点</b><b>
I respect that.</b><b></b>

30:55.890 --> 30:58.530
<b>告诉他除了这件事</b><b>
Just tell him he should ask me anything else.</b><b></b>

30:58.540 --> 31:00.880
<b>我什么都答应</b><b>
This is one favor I can't give him.</b><b></b>

31:00.890 --> 31:04.350
<b>他被拒绝一次后 不会再要求第二次</b><b>
He never asks a second favor when he's been refused the first.</b><b></b>

31:04.360 --> 31:09.680
<b>- 了解? - 你不了解 强尼方亭永远别想演那部电影</b><b>
- Understood? - You don't understand.Johnny Fontane never gets that movie.</b><b></b>

31:10.620 --> 31:12.300
<b>他很适合那个角色</b><b>
That part is perfect for him.</b><b></b>

31:12.310 --> 31:14.390
<b>会让他成为巨星</b><b>
It'll make him a big star.</b><b></b>

31:14.400 --> 31:15.870
<b>但我要让他走投无路</b><b>
I'm gonna run him out of the business.</b><b></b>

31:15.880 --> 31:18.330
<b>我告诉你为什么</b><b>
Let me tell you why.</b><b></b>

31:20.560 --> 31:25.360
<b>强尼毁了一位华尔斯国际公司 最有前途的女星</b><b>
Johnny Fontane ruined one of Woltz International's most valuable proteges.</b><b></b>

31:25.370 --> 31:27.530
<b>五年来我们不断地训练她</b><b>
For five years, we had her under training.</b><b></b>

31:27.540 --> 31:30.750
<b>歌唱课 表演课 跳舞课</b><b>
Singing lessons, acting lessons, dancing lessons.</b><b></b>

31:30.760 --> 31:32.960
<b>我在她身上投资了无数的金钱</b><b>
I spent hundreds of thousands of dollars on her.</b><b></b>

31:32.970 --> 31:35.480
<b>我要让她成为一位巨星</b><b>
I was gonna make her a big star.</b><b></b>

31:35.490 --> 31:38.120
<b>让我更坦白的告诉你</b><b>
And let me be even more frank.</b><b></b>

31:38.130 --> 31:43.480
<b>让你知道我不是铁石心肠 也不是势利眼</b><b>
Just to show you that I'm not a hard-hearted man that it's not all dollars and cents.</b><b></b>

31:43.490 --> 31:47.120
<b>她年轻漂亮 天真无邪</b><b>
She was beautiful. She was young, she was innocent!</b><b></b>

31:47.130 --> 31:51.620
<b>我拥有她就等于拥有全世界</b><b>
She was the greatest piece of ass I've ever had and I've had 'em all over the world!</b><b></b>

31:52.520 --> 31:55.720
<b>然后强尼方亭出现了</b><b>
And then Johnny Fontane comes along</b><b></b>

31:55.730 --> 31:58.930
<b>带着磁性的嗓音 加上意大利的魅力</b><b>
with his olive oil voice and guinea charm.</b><b></b>

31:58.940 --> 32:01.050
<b>把她拐走了</b><b>
And she runs off.</b><b></b>

32:01.810 --> 32:05.820
<b>她跑掉了使我非常难堪</b><b>
She threw it all away just to make me look ridiculous</b><b></b>

32:06.020 --> 32:11.350
<b>而我这种地位的人无法忍受难堪</b><b>
and a man in my position can't afford to be made to look ridiculous!</b><b></b>

32:11.360 --> 32:13.780
<b>你马上给我滚</b><b>
Now you get the hell outta here!</b><b></b>

32:13.790 --> 32:16.560
<b>若是那混球想对我动粗</b><b>
And if that goombah tries any rough stuff</b><b></b>

32:16.570 --> 32:19.070
<b>你告诉他我不是乐队领班</b><b>
you tell him I ain't no bandleader.</b><b></b>

32:19.400 --> 32:23.070
<b>我听过那个故事了</b><b>
Yeah. I heard that story.</b><b></b>

32:23.260 --> 32:25.750
<b>谢谢你的晚餐款待</b><b>
Thank you for the dinner and a very pleasant evening.</b><b></b>

32:27.340 --> 32:29.880
<b>也许你能派车送我去机场</b><b>
If your car could take me to the airport</b><b></b>

32:30.290 --> 32:33.960
<b>柯里昂先生坚持 坏消息要立刻回报</b><b>
Mr. Corleone is a man who insists on hearing bad news immediately.</b><b></b>

34:26.530 --> 34:30.540
<b>- 你不会太累吧? - 汤姆 我在飞机上睡过了</b><b>
- You're not too tired, Tom? - No, I slept on the plane.</b><b></b>

34:30.660 --> 34:32.930
<b>我这里有索拉索的资料</b><b>
I have the Sollozzo notes here.</b><b></b>

34:33.870 --> 34:40.190
<b>众人皆知 索拉索是土耳其人</b><b>
Now Sollozzo is known as ''The Turk.''</b><b></b>

34:40.520 --> 34:42.680
<b>他应该善于用刀</b><b>
He's supposed to be very good with a knife</b><b></b>

34:42.690 --> 34:46.880
<b>但只有发生利益冲突时才会使用</b><b>
but only in matters of business with some sort of reasonable complaint.</b><b></b>

34:47.240 --> 34:49.960
<b>他是做毒品生意的</b><b>
his business is narcotics.</b><b></b>

34:50.290 --> 34:53.740
<b>他们在土耳其种罂粟</b><b>
he has fields in Turkey where they grow the poppy</b><b></b>

34:54.060 --> 34:57.510
<b>在西西里有工厂提炼成海洛因</b><b>
and in Sicily he has the plants to process them into heroin.</b><b></b>

34:58.010 --> 34:59.770
<b>他需要现金</b><b>
Now, he needs cash and he needs protection from the police</b><b></b>

34:59.780 --> 35:03.640
<b>以及在毒品交易时 需要警方的保护</b><b>
for which he gives a piece of the action.</b><b></b>

35:03.650 --> 35:05.550
<b>我无法查出保护费价钱多少</b><b>
I couldn't find out how much.</b><b></b>

35:05.560 --> 35:08.500
<b>在纽约是塔塔基利亚家族 在保护他</b><b>
The Tattaglia family is behind him here in New York.</b><b></b>

35:08.510 --> 35:10.510
<b>他们一定也想分占利益</b><b>
Now, they have to be in it for something.</b><b></b>

35:10.520 --> 35:11.940
<b>山尼柯里昂</b><b>
Santino Corleone.</b><b></b>

35:11.950 --> 35:16.220
<b>他的犯罪前科呢? 一次在意大利 一次在这</b><b>
What about his prison record?Two terms, one in Italy, one here.</b><b></b>

35:16.780 --> 35:19.580
<b>他是众所周知的大毒枭</b><b>
He's known as a top narcotics man.</b><b></b>

35:19.590 --> 35:22.180
<b>山提诺 你认为呢</b><b>
Santino, what do you think?</b><b></b>

35:22.980 --> 35:25.000
<b>白粉可以赚大钱</b><b>
There's a lot of money in that white powder.</b><b></b>

35:27.890 --> 35:29.220
<b>我赞成</b><b>
Tom? I say, yes,</b><b></b>

35:29.260 --> 35:32.260
<b>毒品比什么都好赚</b><b>
there's more money potential in narcotics than anything else we're looking at.</b><b></b>

35:32.270 --> 35:34.940
<b>就算我们不加入 别人也会</b><b>
If we don't get into it, somebody else will.</b><b></b>

35:35.090 --> 35:37.290
<b>也许是五大家族之也许全部都会</b><b>
Maybe one of the five families, maybe all of them.</b><b></b>

35:37.300 --> 35:41.810
<b>他们会用毒品赚到的钱 买通警方和政客</b><b>
With the money they earn they can buy more police and political power.</b><b></b>

35:41.820 --> 35:43.580
<b>到时就会赶上我们</b><b>
Then they come after us.</b><b></b>

35:44.000 --> 35:46.770
<b>现在我们掌握了工会及赌场</b><b>
Now we have the unions, we have the gambling</b><b></b>

35:46.780 --> 35:50.460
<b>而他们却掌握未来最好的东西 毒品</b><b>
and they're the best things to have, but narcotics is a thing of the future.</b><b></b>

35:50.470 --> 35:52.110
<b>我们若不能分一杯羹</b><b>
If we don't get a piece of that action</b><b></b>

35:52.120 --> 35:53.450
<b>我们可能会失去一切</b><b>
we risk everything we have.</b><b></b>

35:53.460 --> 35:56.390
<b>我不是指现在而是在十年之内</b><b>
Not now, but ten years from now.</b><b></b>

36:00.230 --> 36:03.690
<b>你的答案是什么呢?爸爸</b><b>
So? What's your answer gonna be, Pop?</b><b></b>

36:08.000 --> 36:10.500
<b>柯里昂阁下</b><b>
Don Corleone,</b><b></b>

36:11.820 --> 36:14.930
<b>我需要有势力的友人</b><b>
I need a man who has powerful friends.</b><b></b>

36:15.290 --> 36:17.570
<b>我需要一百万元的现金</b><b>
I need a million dollars in cash.</b><b></b>

36:17.910 --> 36:24.700
<b>我需要你手中掌握的政客</b><b>
I need, Don Corleone, those politicians</b><b></b>

36:25.510 --> 36:29.220
<b>三成</b><b>
Thirty percent.</b><b></b>

36:29.540 --> 36:33.250
<b>第一年你就可进帐三四百万元</b><b>
In the first year, your end should be 3, 4 million dollars.</b><b></b>

36:33.530 --> 36:35.300
<b>然后还会增加</b><b>
And then it would go up.</b><b></b>

36:36.750 --> 36:39.690
<b>塔塔基利亚家族 会得到什么好处?</b><b>
And what is the interest for the Tattaglia family?</b><b></b>

36:42.220 --> 36:43.940
<b>我的敬意</b><b>
My compliments.</b><b></b>

36:47.600 --> 36:51.020
<b>我会从我那一份当中分给他们</b><b>
I'll take care of the Tattaglias outta my share.</b><b></b>

36:51.030 --> 36:58.750
<b>我提供财务 政治和法律的保护 可以分到三成</b><b>
So, I receive 30% for finance political influence and legal protection.</b><b></b>

36:58.760 --> 37:00.520
<b>- 这就是你想说的 - 没错</b><b>
- That's what you're telling me. - That's right.</b><b></b>

37:01.930 --> 37:03.360
<b>你为何来找我</b><b>
Why do you come to me?</b><b></b>

37:03.370 --> 37:05.790
<b>我为何值得你这么慷慨</b><b>
Why do I deserve this generosity?</b><b></b>

37:05.800 --> 37:11.030
<b>若你能考虑投资一百万元现金</b><b>
If you consider a million dollars in cash just finance,</b><b></b>

37:11.140 --> 37:13.900
<b>我就会向你敬礼 柯里昂阁下</b><b>
ti saluto, Don Corleone.</b><b></b>

37:24.070 --> 37:29.290
<b>我肯见你是因为 我听说你是个正直的人</b><b>
I said that I would see you because I heard that you were a serious man</b><b></b>

37:29.300 --> 37:31.620
<b>所以我以礼相待</b><b>
to be treated with respect.</b><b></b>

37:36.320 --> 37:40.170
<b>但是我必须拒绝你</b><b>
But I must say no to you.</b><b></b>

37:40.670 --> 37:42.940
<b>我会告诉你原因</b><b>
And I'll give you my reason.</b><b></b>

37:43.620 --> 37:46.850
<b>没错 我是有很多政界的朋友</b><b>
It's true, I have a lot of friends in politics.</b><b></b>

37:47.660 --> 37:50.600
<b>但若他们知道我在搞毒品生意 而不再是赌博时</b><b>
But they wouldn't be friendly very long</b><b></b>

37:50.610 --> 37:52.290
<b>他们就不再是我的朋友</b><b>
if they knew my business was drugs instead of gambling</b><b></b>

37:52.300 --> 37:55.930
<b>他们认为赌博 只是些无伤大雅的事业</b><b>
which they regard as a harmless vice.</b><b></b>

37:55.940 --> 37:57.070
<b>- 但毒品是败坏德性的生意 - 但是柯里昂阁下</b><b>
- But drugs is a dirty business. - No, Don Corleone</b><b></b>

37:57.080 --> 37:59.800
<b>对我而言一个人以何为生</b><b>
It doesn't make any difference to me</b><b></b>

37:59.810 --> 38:02.710
<b>并没有什么差别</b><b>
what a man does for a living, you understand</b><b></b>

38:03.030 --> 38:08.280
<b>但你这种生意…有一点危险性</b><b>
but your business is a little dangerous.</b><b></b>

38:08.290 --> 38:11.050
<b>若你还是担心安全的问题</b><b>
If you're worried about security for your million</b><b></b>

38:11.060 --> 38:12.870
<b>塔塔基利亚会做保证的</b><b>
the Tattaglias will guarantee it.</b><b></b>

38:12.880 --> 38:15.400
<b>你是说塔塔基利亚家族 会保证我们的投资…</b><b>
You're tellin' me the Tattaglias guarantee our investment-</b><b></b>

38:15.410 --> 38:17.160
<b>等一下</b><b>
Wait a minute.</b><b></b>

38:23.570 --> 38:28.280
<b>你看我把孩子都给宠坏了</b><b>
I have a sentimental weakness for my children and I spoil them, as you can see.</b><b></b>

38:28.290 --> 38:30.450
<b>他们说话非常没有分寸</b><b>
They talk when they should listen.</b><b></b>

38:30.460 --> 38:33.060
<b>但总之</b><b>
But anyway</b><b></b>

38:33.070 --> 38:35.320
<b>索拉索先生 我的决定还是不行</b><b>
Signor Sollozzo, my ''no'' is final</b><b></b>

38:35.330 --> 38:37.460
<b>我要恭喜你的生意</b><b>
and I wish to congratulate you on your new business.</b><b></b>

38:37.470 --> 38:40.930
<b>我知道你会很成功我祝你好运</b><b>
I know you'll do very well, and good luck to you</b><b></b>

38:40.940 --> 38:45.040
<b>尤其是你的生意不会与我的冲突</b><b>
especially since your interests don't conflict with mine.</b><b></b>

38:45.230 --> 38:46.820
<b>谢谢</b><b>
Thank you.</b><b></b>

39:06.550 --> 39:08.090
<b>山提诺</b><b>
Santino.</b><b></b>

39:08.380 --> 39:10.170
<b>到这来</b><b>
Come here.</b><b></b>

39:12.500 --> 39:14.440
<b>你是怎么回事</b><b>
What's the matter with you?</b><b></b>

39:14.590 --> 39:19.310
<b>我看你和女孩子胡搞之后 脑子退化了</b><b>
I think your brain is going soft from all that comedy you're playing with that young girl.</b><b></b>

39:19.320 --> 39:23.380
<b>别让外人知道你在想什么</b><b>
Never tell anybody outside the family what you're thinking again.</b><b></b>

39:24.800 --> 39:26.380
<b>走吧</b><b>
Go on.</b><b></b>

39:29.830 --> 39:32.590
<b>汤姆 这是什么乱七八糟的</b><b>
Tom, what- What is this nonsense?</b><b></b>

39:32.600 --> 39:36.140
<b>那是强尼送的 他主演了那部新电影</b><b>
It's from Johnny. He's starring in that new film.</b><b></b>

39:36.470 --> 39:39.880
<b>好了 把它拿走</b><b>
Well, take it away.</b><b></b>

39:39.890 --> 39:41.650
<b>把它放到那去</b><b>
Take it over there.</b><b></b>

39:42.720 --> 39:44.300
<b>还有</b><b>
And</b><b></b>

39:45.060 --> 39:47.610
<b>叫路卡布拉西到这来</b><b>
tell Luca Brasi to come in.</b><b></b>

39:53.490 --> 39:56.820
<b>我对这索拉索有点担心</b><b>
I'm a little worried about this Sollozzo fellow.</b><b></b>

39:56.920 --> 40:00.290
<b>我要你弄清楚他在耍什么把戏</b><b>
I want you to find out what he's got under his fingernails.</b><b></b>

40:00.830 --> 40:04.500
<b>到塔塔基利亚那边去</b><b>
Go to the Tattaglias</b><b></b>

40:04.510 --> 40:09.660
<b>让他们以为你与我们家族不融洽</b><b>
and make them think that you're not too happy with our family</b><b></b>

40:10.160 --> 40:13.010
<b>尽量查</b><b>
and find out what you can.</b><b></b>

40:30.920 --> 40:33.380
<b>我买了东西给令堂</b><b>
And I got something for your mother and for Sonny</b><b></b>

40:33.390 --> 40:38.140
<b>还有给弗雷多的领带 给汤姆的钢笔</b><b>
and a tie for Freddy and Tom Hagen got the Reynolds pen.</b><b></b>

40:38.480 --> 40:42.490
<b>- 你圣诞节想要什么? - 我只要你</b><b>
- What do you want for Christmas? - Me? Oh, just you.</b><b></b>

41:13.520 --> 41:15.330
<b>醒醒 弗雷多</b><b>
Andiamo, Fredo.</b><b></b>

41:15.340 --> 41:17.320
<b>叫保利备车 我们要走了</b><b>
Tell Paulie to get the car. We're going.</b><b></b>

41:17.330 --> 41:18.890
<b>好的 爸</b><b>
Okay, Pa.</b><b></b>

41:18.900 --> 41:22.700
<b>我来开车 保利今早生病了</b><b>
I'll have to get it myself. Paulie called in sick this morning.</b><b></b>

41:24.710 --> 41:27.430
<b>保利是个好孩子 我不介意自己开车</b><b>
Paulie's a good kid. I don't mind gettin' the car.</b><b></b>

41:31.280 --> 41:33.950
<b>谢谢</b><b>
Thank you.</b><b></b>

42:16.210 --> 42:21.100
<b>- 路卡 我是布诺塔塔基利亚 - 我知道</b><b>
- Luca,I am Bruno Tattaglia. - I know.</b><b></b>

42:21.300 --> 42:22.940
<b>想喝杯威士忌吗?</b><b>
Scotch?</b><b></b>

42:22.950 --> 42:24.460
<b>先暖和一下</b><b>
Prewar.</b><b></b>

42:24.470 --> 42:26.480
<b>我不喝酒</b><b></b>

42:30.550 --> 42:32.090
<b>你知道我是谁吗?</b><b>
You know who I am?</b><b></b>

42:32.100 --> 42:33.570
<b>我认识你</b><b>
Yeah.</b><b></b>

42:33.580 --> 42:37.690
<b>你和塔塔基利亚家族谈过了 对吧?</b><b></b>

42:38.490 --> 42:44.040
<b>我认为我们可以一起做些生意</b><b></b>

42:44.960 --> 42:47.780
<b>我需要像你这么壮的人</b><b></b>

42:47.790 --> 42:55.450
<b>我听说你与柯里昂家族不和</b><b></b>

42:55.730 --> 42:57.490
<b>想加入我们吗?</b><b></b>

42:57.500 --> 42:59.750
<b>我能得到什么好处</b><b></b>

42:59.990 --> 43:03.960
<b>起薪五万元</b><b></b>

43:07.190 --> 43:09.300
<b>还不坏</b><b></b>

43:09.580 --> 43:13.380
<b>同意了</b><b></b>

